@startuml ch14-stella-multiagente
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam defaultFontName "Noto Sans"
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ComponentBackgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam ComponentBorderColor #333333
skinparam ArrowColor #333333

component "_CONTEXT.md\n(fonte di verita, condiviso in git)" as CTX #E8F4FD
component "AGENTS.md\n(contratto comune)" as AGENTS

component "CLAUDE.md" as CLAUDE
component "GEMINI.md" as GEMINI
component "OPENCLAW.md" as OPENCLAW
component "VISUALSTUDIO.md" as VS
component ".github/copilot-instructions.md" as COPILOT

CLAUDE --> AGENTS : importa
GEMINI --> AGENTS : importa
OPENCLAW --> AGENTS : importa
VS --> AGENTS : importa
COPILOT ..> AGENTS : adotta i principi\n(non importa)

AGENTS --> CTX : legge lo stato

note bottom of CTX
  Tutti gli agenti leggono
  lo stesso _CONTEXT.md:
  contesto allineato senza
  briefing manuale.
end note

@enduml
